[{"Code":"en","Title":"Set up webhooks","Slug":"bill-payments-set-up-webhooks","ContentType":2,"Content":"<p data-block-id=\"e3916ec0-82da-4820-a4c6-8cfe3445305a\">In our Bill Payments API flows, all payments events will have notifications that you can subscribe to. Your system should be set up to receive our webhooks even if you only use flows where we update the payment statuses synchronously.</p><p data-block-id=\"fdbefe51-8303-4ac1-bc29-3e00540066e7\">In particular, being subscribed to our <code>Bill Payment</code> webhooks can help your system know whether a bill payment has happened in real time for payments where end users.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"68e3b468-5240-41a1-ac72-189aaab39040\">Saving your webhook endpoints with Xendit</h2><ol data-block-id=\"5624d09f-3240-4c77-9533-6c520fe98f8c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"95002ca1-7139-41a3-a728-372508767e82\"><p data-block-id=\"6f06de9c-6fcd-4571-b51d-b011ac0bb5e8\">Click <strong>Settings</strong> on your sidebar</p></li><li data-block-id=\"95c6275a-6eef-45d8-924b-6f2c96468fa0\"><p data-block-id=\"07c49fa3-291d-429a-a9d7-0a00a9a9c552\">Click <strong>Webhooks </strong>on the sub menu</p></li><li data-block-id=\"0529c5d2-b83f-4394-b394-10d9adb666c0\"><p data-block-id=\"a26a1173-88d2-4eec-a245-fc51de76ee72\">Update the webhook url fields shown in the screenshot below and click <strong>Test and save</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"68347260-84c3-4705-916c-dbe0c60c2e82\"><p data-block-id=\"b13218c6-c5ab-4e76-a466-a508b295e1f2\">Validate that you’ve received the exact test notification in your system</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"d3d8324c-d5ca-419b-abee-14c1ca254b5c\"><img data-block-id=\"f8fdac62-82a5-4035-94d0-4f7489ee7383\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(113).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"3f7b0d76-ceaf-4bca-9ed7-3a0eefd428ed\">Available webhook endpoints</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"906\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:906px;width:906px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:453px;\"><col style=\"width:453px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"f79ed1c8-bcb5-4646-861d-3ab939c74a72\">Topic</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"477f7864-34e4-4e8f-be13-a420ec310086\">Description</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"ad6e6c15-684d-453e-83c1-245967792cf4\">Bill Payments</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"89bae961-9f0a-428b-a25d-e9a5aea863ba\">Notification event when bill payment is succeeded or failed</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"9e4a4fcf-26cc-49ba-a661-8612df7383af\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Set up webhooks","Description":null},{"Code":"id","Title":"Atur webhooks","Slug":"set-up-webhooks-1","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"e3916ec0-82da-4820-a4c6-8cfe3445305a\">Dalam alur Bill Payments API kami, semua event pembayaran akan memiliki notifikasi yang dapat Anda subscribe. Sistem Anda harus diatur untuk menerima webhook kami bahkan jika Anda hanya menggunakan alur di mana kami memperbarui status pembayaran secara sinkron.</p><p data-block-id=\"fdbefe51-8303-4ac1-bc29-3e00540066e7\">Secara khusus, dengan men-subscribe webhook <code>Bill Payment</code> kami dapat membantu sistem Anda mengetahui apakah pembayaran tagihan telah terjadi secara real-time untuk pembayaran yang dilakukan oleh pengguna akhir.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"68e3b468-5240-41a1-ac72-189aaab39040\">Menyimpan endpoint webhook Anda dengan Xendit</h2><ol data-block-id=\"5624d09f-3240-4c77-9533-6c520fe98f8c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"95002ca1-7139-41a3-a728-372508767e82\"><p data-block-id=\"6f06de9c-6fcd-4571-b51d-b011ac0bb5e8\">Klik <strong>Settings</strong> di sidebar Anda</p></li><li data-block-id=\"95c6275a-6eef-45d8-924b-6f2c96468fa0\"><p data-block-id=\"07c49fa3-291d-429a-a9d7-0a00a9a9c552\">Klik <strong>Webhooks </strong>pada sub menu</p></li><li data-block-id=\"0529c5d2-b83f-4394-b394-10d9adb666c0\"><p data-block-id=\"a26a1173-88d2-4eec-a245-fc51de76ee72\">Perbarui kolom URL webhook yang ditampilkan pada screenshot di bawah dan klik <strong>Test and save</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"68347260-84c3-4705-916c-dbe0c60c2e82\"><p data-block-id=\"b13218c6-c5ab-4e76-a466-a508b295e1f2\">Validasi bahwa Anda telah menerima notifikasi tes yang sama persis di sistem Anda</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"d3d8324c-d5ca-419b-abee-14c1ca254b5c\"><img data-block-id=\"f8fdac62-82a5-4035-94d0-4f7489ee7383\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(113).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link=\"\" newtab=\"\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"3f7b0d76-ceaf-4bca-9ed7-3a0eefd428ed\">Endpoint webhook yang tersedia</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"906\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:906px;width:906px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:453px;\"><col style=\"width:453px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"f79ed1c8-bcb5-4646-861d-3ab939c74a72\">Topik</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"477f7864-34e4-4e8f-be13-a420ec310086\">Deskripsi</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"ad6e6c15-684d-453e-83c1-245967792cf4\">Bill Payments</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"89bae961-9f0a-428b-a25d-e9a5aea863ba\">Event notifikasi ketika pembayaran tagihan berhasil atau gagal</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"9e4a4fcf-26cc-49ba-a661-8612df7383af\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Atur webhooks","Description":null},{"Code":"th","Title":"ตั้งค่า webhook","Slug":"set-up-webhooks-1","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"e3916ec0-82da-4820-a4c6-8cfe3445305a\">ในขั้นตอนการทำงานของ Bill Payments API ของเรา เหตุการณ์การชำระเงินทั้งหมดจะมีข้อความแจ้งเตือนที่คุณสามารถสมัครรับได้ ระบบของคุณควรได้รับการตั้งค่าให้รับ webhooks ของเรา แม้ว่าคุณจะใช้เฉพาะขั้นตอนที่เราอัปเดตสถานะการชำระเงินแบบ synchronously ก็ตาม</p><p data-block-id=\"fdbefe51-8303-4ac1-bc29-3e00540066e7\">โดยเฉพาะอย่างยิ่ง การสมัครรับ <code>Bill Payment</code> webhooks ของเราสามารถช่วยให้ระบบของคุณทราบได้ว่ามีการชำระบิลเกิดขึ้นแบบ real time หรือไม่ สำหรับการชำระเงินที่ผู้ใช้ปลายทาง</p><h2 data-block-id=\"68e3b468-5240-41a1-ac72-189aaab39040\">การบันทึก webhook endpoints ของคุณกับ Xendit</h2><ol data-block-id=\"5624d09f-3240-4c77-9533-6c520fe98f8c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"95002ca1-7139-41a3-a728-372508767e82\"><p data-block-id=\"6f06de9c-6fcd-4571-b51d-b011ac0bb5e8\">คลิก <strong>Settings</strong> บนแถบด้านข้างของคุณ</p></li><li data-block-id=\"95c6275a-6eef-45d8-924b-6f2c96468fa0\"><p data-block-id=\"07c49fa3-291d-429a-a9d7-0a00a9a9c552\">คลิก <strong>Webhooks </strong>บนเมนูย่อย</p></li><li data-block-id=\"0529c5d2-b83f-4394-b394-10d9adb666c0\"><p data-block-id=\"a26a1173-88d2-4eec-a245-fc51de76ee72\">อัปเดตช่อง URL ของ webhook ที่แสดงในภาพหน้าจอด้านล่าง แล้วคลิก <strong>Test and save</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"68347260-84c3-4705-916c-dbe0c60c2e82\"><p data-block-id=\"b13218c6-c5ab-4e76-a466-a508b295e1f2\">ตรวจสอบว่าคุณได้รับข้อความแจ้งเตือนทดสอบที่ถูกต้องในระบบของคุณ</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"d3d8324c-d5ca-419b-abee-14c1ca254b5c\"><img data-block-id=\"f8fdac62-82a5-4035-94d0-4f7489ee7383\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(113).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"3f7b0d76-ceaf-4bca-9ed7-3a0eefd428ed\">Available webhook endpoints</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"906\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:906px;width:906px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:453px;\"><col style=\"width:453px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"f79ed1c8-bcb5-4646-861d-3ab939c74a72\">Topic (หัวข้อ)</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"477f7864-34e4-4e8f-be13-a420ec310086\">Description (คำอธิบาย)</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"ad6e6c15-684d-453e-83c1-245967792cf4\">Bill Payments</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"89bae961-9f0a-428b-a25d-e9a5aea863ba\">เหตุการณ์แจ้งเตือนเมื่อการชำระบิลสำเร็จหรือล้มเหลว</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"9e4a4fcf-26cc-49ba-a661-8612df7383af\"></p>","SeoTitle":"ตั้งค่า webhook","Description":null},{"Code":"es-mx","Title":"Configurar webhooks","Slug":"set-up-webhooks-1","ContentType":2,"Content":"<style> p[data-block-id] {font-size:1rem;} ul li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ul[data-type=\"taskList\"] li div p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} ol li p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0;} table tbody th p[data-block-id] { margin-bottom: 0;} blockquote p[data-block-id] {margin-bottom: 0 !important;}  p[data-block-id]:empty::after {content: \"\\00A0\";} </style><p data-block-id=\"e3916ec0-82da-4820-a4c6-8cfe3445305a\">En nuestros flujos de la API de Bill Payments, todos los eventos de pago tendrán notificaciones a las que usted puede suscribirse. Su sistema debe estar configurado para recibir nuestros webhooks incluso si solo utiliza flujos donde actualizamos los estados de pago de forma síncrona.</p><p data-block-id=\"fdbefe51-8303-4ac1-bc29-3e00540066e7\">En particular, estar suscrito a nuestros webhooks de <code>Bill Payment</code> puede ayudar a su sistema a saber si un pago de factura ha ocurrido en tiempo real para pagos donde los usuarios finales.</p><h2 data-block-id=\"68e3b468-5240-41a1-ac72-189aaab39040\">Guardar sus endpoints de webhook con Xendit</h2><ol data-block-id=\"5624d09f-3240-4c77-9533-6c520fe98f8c\" start=\"1\"><li data-block-id=\"95002ca1-7139-41a3-a728-372508767e82\"><p data-block-id=\"6f06de9c-6fcd-4571-b51d-b011ac0bb5e8\">Haga clic en <strong>Settings</strong> en su barra lateral</p></li><li data-block-id=\"95c6275a-6eef-45d8-924b-6f2c96468fa0\"><p data-block-id=\"07c49fa3-291d-429a-a9d7-0a00a9a9c552\">Haga clic en <strong>Webhooks </strong>en el submenú</p></li><li data-block-id=\"0529c5d2-b83f-4394-b394-10d9adb666c0\"><p data-block-id=\"a26a1173-88d2-4eec-a245-fc51de76ee72\">Actualice los campos de URL de webhook que se muestran en la captura de pantalla a continuación y haga clic en <strong>Test and save</strong></p></li><li data-block-id=\"68347260-84c3-4705-916c-dbe0c60c2e82\"><p data-block-id=\"b13218c6-c5ab-4e76-a466-a508b295e1f2\">Valide que ha recibido la notificación de prueba exacta en su sistema</p></li></ol><p data-block-id=\"d3d8324c-d5ca-419b-abee-14c1ca254b5c\"><img data-block-id=\"f8fdac62-82a5-4035-94d0-4f7489ee7383\" src=\"https://cdn.document360.io/217abc43-8677-41fb-a81d-fceeb1fa0358/Images/Documentation/image(113).png\" class=\"adv-wysiwyg-img\" mediatype=\"img\" alt=\"\" width=\"auto\" height=\"auto\" dataalign=\"left\" datadisplay=\"flex\" data-type=\"media-content\" fixaspectratio=\"false\" autoaspectratio=\"true\" shadow=\"no\" border=\"no\" round=\"no\" link newtab style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></p><h2 data-block-id=\"3f7b0d76-ceaf-4bca-9ed7-3a0eefd428ed\">Endpoints de webhook disponibles</h2><div data-type=\"table-content\"><table width=\"906\" class=\"editor360-table\" borderstyle=\"solid\" style=\"max-width:906px;width:906px;\"><colgroup><col style=\"width:453px;\"><col style=\"width:453px;\"></colgroup><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"f79ed1c8-bcb5-4646-861d-3ab939c74a72\">Tema</p></th><th colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"477f7864-34e4-4e8f-be13-a420ec310086\">Descripción</p></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"ad6e6c15-684d-453e-83c1-245967792cf4\">Bill Payments</p></td><td colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" colwidth=\"453\"><p data-block-id=\"89bae961-9f0a-428b-a25d-e9a5aea863ba\">Evento de notificación cuando el pago de factura es exitoso o fallido</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p data-block-id=\"9e4a4fcf-26cc-49ba-a661-8612df7383af\"></p>","SeoTitle":"Configurar webhooks","Description":null}]